## â–¶ï¸ Usage
Once installed, simply run:
```
simple-fastapi-backend-server
```
The server will start at http://localhost:8000.

## ğŸ“‹ Endpoints
- `GET /`
    ```
    { "message": "API is running" }
    ```
- `POST /register`

    **Request body:**
    ```
    {
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "secret"
    }
    ```
    **Response:**
    ```
    {
    "message": "User registered successfully",
    "user": {
        "username": "johndoe",
        "password": "secret"
    }
    }
    ```
- `POST /login`

    **Request body:**
    ```
    {
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "secret"
    }
    ```
    **Response:**
    ```
    {
    "message": "User logged in successfully",
    "user": {
        "username": "johndoe",
        "password": "secret"
    }
    }
    ```
